        "about_title": "About ChelCheleh",
        "about_intro": "Welcome to ChelCheleh Content Management System! ChelCheleh is a lightweight, fast, and powerful CMS built with Python and the FastAPI framework. This system is designed for those seeking a simple and efficient solution for managing their website, without the need for complex configurations or heavy database dependencies.",
        "about_flatfile_title": "Flat-File Architecture",
        "about_flatfile": "One of ChelCheleh's unique features is its Flat-File architecture. Unlike traditional content management systems like WordPress that require MySQL or PostgreSQL databases, ChelCheleh stores all information in JSON files. This approach offers multiple advantages: installation is extremely simple, no database management is needed, backup is as easy as copying files, and loading speed for small to medium websites is very high.",
        "about_storage_title": "How Data is Stored",
        "about_storage": "ChelCheleh uses a smart storage system that maintains data in organized JSON files. Pages, blog posts, settings, user information, menus, and other content are each stored in separate files. This structure makes data management and maintenance simple, and allows you to easily edit files when needed.",
        "about_tech_title": "Technologies Used",
        "about_tech": "ChelCheleh is built using modern technologies: FastAPI as the web framework providing high speed and security, Jinja2 for the templating engine, and Python 3.10+ as the core language. The system uses a modular architecture that enables development and addition of new features.",
        "about_features_title": "Main Features",
        "about_features": "ChelCheleh includes complete features for website management: page management with HTML and Markdown support, blog system with categories and tags, file and media management, user system with different roles, various templates, full support for Persian language and RTL, and automatic update system.",
        "about_security_title": "Security",
        "about_security": "Security is taken seriously in ChelCheleh. The system uses CSRF tokens for attack protection, secure password hashing algorithms, failed login attempt limiting, and HTTP security headers.",
